metadata.name: Avenue !
metadata.description:
For the longest time I have used fire as a symbol for starting anew. 

To burn away is to shed my skin, to let go of the past. 

This collection of four is a practice of minimalism, and a transition into a new era for me. As some may have noticed, the alias of Alhucard is being transcended. I am ready to move forward in my creativity under my own name. I am Trizton, not a character. I am setting fire to old patterns and thought processes, and peacefully moving forward.
